HGTV Urban Oasis 2017 Giveaway



Egypt Sherrod leads the renovation of the HGTV Urban Oasis 2017, located near the Great Smoky Mountains in Knoxville, Tennessee. She teams up with designer Brian Patrick Flynn to revive the time-worn, vintage home and transform it into a beautiful modern oasis. Situated in the heart of a charming and highly desirable historic neighborhood, this home and cash prize will be given away to one lucky winner.




Original Air Date: 06-Oct-2017
